g expression) {\n            // Parameters are accepted so XSLTProcess can configure this liaison.\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void transform(File infile, File outfile) throws IOException {\n            assertThat(stylesheet).isNotNull();\n            Files.copy(infile.toPath(), outfile.toPath());\n        }\n    }\n","newText":""}]}
